      <title>印度央行放松投资限制后银行股上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/lenders-rally-after-india-s-central-bank-eases-investment-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行放宽了对一种独特投资类型的资本要求，此举可能会释放更多资金用于贷款，周四印度银行和影子银行股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/lenders-rally-after-india-s-central-bank-eases-investment-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 08:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
